title: Zeider-Man 2/3: Rush Limbaugh, Madonna, Nick Lachey, Dumbledore

description:
On this edition of Zeider-Man Jack and Miles discuss Rush Limbaugh announcing he has advanced Lung Cancer, Madonna is being sued by some fans, Nick Lachey opening up about former relationships, and Dumbledore being used in the Senate.
